we eventually come to the point where `newDictionary=[[A, B, B, C], [D, E, F, E]]` and we have to try to insert `[E, A]`. Here both groups from `newDictionary` will have to be merged together.&lt;br&gt;
This then results in the output of `[[A, B, C, D, E, F]]`, where both groups are merged and removed duplicates.

